    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267970/extras/7d3cbc0a7fa4cd937de67cec35825f55.avif?t=1732627533\" width=600 height=253 /></span><br>Nekopirate is a story driven action-platformer featuring short challenging levels, colorful graphics and a heartfelt story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267970/extras/9f341b15184fe6c362e2ccf3e121e3e5.poster.avif?t=1732627533\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267970/extras/9f341b15184fe6c362e2ccf3e121e3e5.webm?t=1732627533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267970/extras/9f341b15184fe6c362e2ccf3e121e3e5.mp4?t=1732627533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Nina is a nekopirate and the daughter of legendary pirate Bartholomeow Williams. When her father falls ill it is up to Nina to find a cure. But her quest will soon prove to be more challenging than expected, when the only known cure for his illness is a mystical flower known as Lágrima de la Luna.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267970/extras/cc716352c8b060f76213e1b585883d17.avif?t=1732627533\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Explore the Caribbean Sea, Run inside a volcano, find love in an underwater Mermaid City, defeat a giant Rubber Duck, all while trying to escape an island where everything is trying to kill you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267970/extras/c26e9f5ff6e946a5f7feaf7edb0d0a3e.poster.avif?t=1732627533\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267970/extras/c26e9f5ff6e946a5f7feaf7edb0d0a3e.webm?t=1732627533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267970/extras/c26e9f5ff6e946a5f7feaf7edb0d0a3e.mp4?t=1732627533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br>- Over 40 hand-crafted levels<br>- 4 different pirate-themed locations<br>- Fast-paced platforming gameplay<br>- Unlockable weapons<br>- Tons of collectables and side quests<br>- Beautiful artwork<br>- Giant bosses and mini games<br>- A funny and emotional story about love and determination<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267970/extras/2ea0a4eb92ca5b35a7e798c5a3a7d008.poster.avif?t=1732627533\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267970/extras/2ea0a4eb92ca5b35a7e798c5a3a7d008.webm?t=1732627533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
